WEBVTT

00:28.255 --> 00:29.737
Taste of Your Own Medicine

00:30.526 --> 00:32.727
It means unpleasant treatment...

00:33.037 --> 00:35.445
...that is like the treatment you have given other people.

00:39.835 --> 00:41.341
He kept on teasing people...

00:41.747 --> 00:46.023
...but he finally got a taste of his own medicine when the others fought back.

00:51.296 --> 00:53.251
He keeps on laughing at other people;...

00:53.775 --> 00:56.121
...someone should give him a taste of his own medicine.

01:00.361 --> 01:04.946
She got a taste of her own medicine when everyone became rude to her.

